replies.body:
klepto simply shouldnt exist.  If you see the way that it is used the majority of the time, IMO it doesnt bring healthy interactions to LoL.

Lane bullies (mostly ranged ones ie. {{champion:85}} {{champion:126}} etc) take it in matchups that they will already win, so by continuing their play patterns where they already win lane and poke, they get more gold than their opponent.

And its also used by champs with really weak early games who can proc it (again, from range) to circumvent their weak early games by getting more gold.  IE {{champion:10}} {{champion:41}}
